Buddy as a Service (baas) is a jabber/wave robot, using Yahoo Boss API, Google API and other services to do some stuff for you.

requirements:

- Universal Feed Parser ( http://www.feedparser.org )
- Twisted Words ( http://twistedmatrix.com/trac/wiki/TwistedWords )
- if running as wave robot: wave-robot-python-client ( http://code.google.com/p/wave-robot-python-client/ )

xmpp demo:

If you want to see BaaS in action, add baas@borho.net to your jabber contacts.

wave-robot:

add buddyasaservice@appspot.com to your contacts

usage:

type 'help' for available commands

news:word - searches for news
web:word - websearch
blip:song - search for songs on blip.fm
tlate:word #en - translates the word in german in english, #LANG sepcifies the target lang
bm:tag - searches bm.doomicile
example:foo - gives you a bla for a foo
blog:word - blog search via twingly
micro:word - microblog search via twingly

Some commands (news,web) can be combined with #de, examples:
news:hamburg #de
web:xmpp #de

A translation needs the target language specified by a hashtag
tlate:Wie gehts?  #en
tlate:Wie gehts?  #es
tlate:How do you do? #de

